    "a83d5716-a698-4eb4-9598-233853bf712b": {
      "type": "testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "template--15972757405866__a83d5716-a698-4eb4-9598-233853bf712b-166883761837539b17-0": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p><strong>The Camper Van, Natural</strong></p><p><strong>Absolutely Stunning!</strong></p><p>I've been eyeing this toy for two years but we just couldn't buy it. This year we decided to make it our children's one big gift and family chipped in. I am so excited and I know they will be too! We got the Olli Ella magical creatures for my daughters upcoming birthday and they fit nicely inside the camper van. The mini stove, pot, and furniture are sweet. The wood is solid and beautiful. It coasts nicely on the floor with the center caster. It is definitely a solid, well built toy.</p>",
            "author": "K.",
            "author_info": ""
          }
        },
        "template--15972757405866__a83d5716-a698-4eb4-9598-233853bf712b-166883761837539b17-1": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p><strong>The Kitchen Cupboard</strong></p><p><strong>Absolutely beautiful</strong></p><p>This piece of children’s furniture looks amazing in our home! It is both beautiful and practical. Our son’s little bowls, cups, flatware and plates fit neatly inside. What a wonderful piece to add to our dining area! I know it will be a treasured piece for years to come!</p>",
            "author": "A.B.",
            "author_info": ""
          }
        },
        "template--15972757405866__a83d5716-a698-4eb4-9598-233853bf712b-166883761837539b17-2": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p><strong>Wooden Tray </strong></p><p><strong>So many uses</strong></p><p>Planning on using for kitchen play and for carrying snacks to and from the table. Breakfast in bed, delivering food to sick kids, keeping crafts organized…I can think of so many uses already.</p>",
            "author": "S.B.",
            "author_info": ""
          }
        },
        "template--15972757405866__a83d5716-a698-4eb4-9598-233853bf712b-166883761837539b17-3": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p><strong>Pirates Island</strong></p><p><strong>Stunnin’ toy, Matey!</strong></p><p>Gorgeous toy. It is so well-crafted. I absolutely love the trap door. I can’t wait to gift it to my son for Christmas!</p>",
            "author": "D.H.",
            "author_info": ""
          }
        },
        "template--15972757405866__a83d5716-a698-4eb4-9598-233853bf712b-166883761837539b17-4": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p><strong>Truck with Trailer</strong></p><p><strong>Better than Expected!</strong></p><p>I purchased this as a Christmas gift for my son, and I can’t wait for him to see it! It’s absolutely beautiful and such great quality. It’s going to be one of those pieces that lasts for generations.</p>",
            "author": "Jessica",
            "author_info": ""
          }
        }
      },
